# Design Specifications

| Part    | Key Dimensions        | Material    |
|---------|-----------------------|-------------|
| Body    | Φ194 × 30 mm, R50(3x) | Aluminum    |
| Shaft   | Ø28.9 × 247.6 mm      | Stainless   |
| Arm     | R63.75, 112.5 mm (2x) | Steel       |
| Plate1  | 130.5 × 37.7 mm       | Steel       |
| Plate2  | 100 × 6.5 mm          | Steel       |
| Bolt    | Ø15.1 × 38 mm         | Steel       |

